flowchart TD
    A[Anki loads add-on] --> B[__init__.py registers hooks and menu action]
    B --> C[User opens Browser]
    C --> D[register_browser_instance stores current browser]
    D --> E[User selects note]
    E --> F[editor_will_load_note reads browser and config]
    F --> G[Hide or reset JS is prepared]
    G --> H[apply_field_visibility runs on live editor]
    H --> I{Hiding active for this note type?}
    I -- Yes --> J[Hide non-allowed field containers]
    I -- No --> K[Show all field containers]
    J --> L[User clicks Show Fields]
    K --> L
    L --> M[toggle_field_visibility updates config]
    M --> N[Note type added to field_visibility_disabled]
    N --> O[Reset visibility and show all fields]
    O --> P[User clicks Hide Fields]
    P --> Q[toggle_field_visibility updates config again]
    Q --> R[Note type removed from field_visibility_disabled]
    R --> S[Hide JS is applied again]
    S --> T[Configured fields remain visible]
